<section class="header">
  <div class="menu1"><Menumobil /></div>
  <div class="menu"><Menu /></div>

  <div class="flex">
    <div>
      <Image class="pic" src={venstre} alt="venstre" />
    </div>
    <div>
      <h3>I AM PROTECTED</h3>
      <Image class="pic3" src={højre} alt="venstre" />
      <p class="hero">
        Luxuriously soothing and deeply moisturizing, it swiftly penetrates the
        skin, making it your go-to for daytime radiance.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section class="citat">
  <div>
    <h4>
      "I AM" cultivates awareness and empowers out consumers to take an active <br
      />
      role in their journey, embracing their inner energy and guidance to become
      <br />
      self-experts"
    </h4>
  </div>
</section>
<section class="bestseller">
  <div class="bestseller1">
    <h2 class="best">BEST SELLER</h2>
    <h3 class="bestseller3">
      Introducing our Bestseller - our faceoils Bestseller Face Oil
    </h3>
    <p class="bestseller2">
      Some of the love-infused benefits: Radiance-Boosting Raspberry Seed Oil:
      Enriched with potent antioxidants, this elixir strengthens your skin's
      defenses against daily stressors, ensuring a flawless, luminous
      complexion. Balancing Squalene Formula: Experience the magic of balanced
      hydration as this lightweight elixir harmonizes your skin's natural oils,
      leaving it resilient, supple, and deeply nourished. Luxurious Pequi Oil
      Blend: Indulge in the ultimate skin treat! Our blend of pequi oil, rich in
      essential fatty acids and vitamins, deeply nourishes your skin, unveiling
      a captivating glow and lasting vitality.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div>
    <Image class="pic1" src={forside} alt="højre" />
  </div>
</section>
<section>
  <h2 class="produkter">OTHER PRODUCTS</h2>
  <div class="produkt">
    <div>
      <Image class="pic2" src={pro3} alt="pro1" />
      <p class="tekst">I AM HEALING <br /> FACE OIL <br /> 415 kr</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <Image class="pic2" src={pro1} alt="pro1" />
      <p class="tekst">
        I AM PURIFIED <br />
        FACE WASH <br />
        225 kr
